Experimental Orchestra Opcodes and GEN Routines



  Experimental Orchestra Opcodes


    The following opcodes are deprecatedrequire a nVidia GPU to be
    present. They are distributed with the hope that they may be
    useful, and to encourage the use of parallelise in audio
    processing.  Some of the new opcodes proform the same process as
    conventional existing oes but some are new.



